title: CDDIS_DORIS_products_stcd
summary: Station position time series solutions in DORIS Station Coordinate Difference (STCD) format derived from analysis of Doppler Orbitography by Radiopositioning Integrated on Satellite (DORIS) data. These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International DORIS Service (IDS).
